Download the script from https://www.dwservice.net/en/

For linux 

install the downloaded sh script

sudo chmod +x dwagent.sh

sudo ./dwagent.sh

install and follow the prompts until the section where you add a code..

Create an account on dwagent
Login

Add a group
Add an agent - this will generate a code

Insert the code in the machine where you installed the .sh file

Done